where formula_79, formula_80 and formula_81.

formula_82 and formula_83 can be identified as the variance matrices of the marginal distributions for formula_84 and formula_85 respectively.

If formula_4 and formula_9 are jointly normally distributed,
formula_88
then the conditional distribution for formula_9 given formula_4 is given by
